Description:
    Generates a rake task that will be included at the end of the deployment task.  An optional
    parameter with the task description is recommended. An optional group
    parameter with the task group is recommended.

Example:
    rails generate after_party:task task_name --group=after_load --description=optional_description_of_the_task

    This will create:
        lib/tasks/deployment/<timestamp>_data_update.rake
